{{#if firstName}}<p style='color:#4b5563;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 16px 0;'>Hi {{firstName}},</p>{{/if}}
<p style='color:#4b5563;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 16px 0;'>Your charging session was stopped because the site is going into a scheduled maintenance window.</p>
<p style='color:#1a1a1a;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 16px 0;'><strong>Session:</strong> {{sessionId}}<br/><strong>Maintenance event:</strong> {{maintenanceEventId}}<br/><strong>Expected end:</strong> {{plannedEndAt}}{{#if reason}}<br/><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}{{/if}}</p>
<p style='color:#6b7280;line-height:1.6;margin:0;font-size:14px;'>You will only be charged for energy actually delivered. We apologize for the inconvenience.</p>